  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/24/whatsapp-voice-communication/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/c75e6fe836b0d822e593135587a6af79/whatsapp-logo.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n在被 Facebook 以 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/20/google-offered-10-billion-for-whatsapp/\">190 亿美元收购</a>后，作用 4.65 亿月活跃用户的 WhatsApp 现在又宣布了<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/20/why-did-facebook-spend-19-billion-on-a-messaging-app-video/\">新的动作</a>。在 MWC 2014 的现场，CEO Jan Koum 在接受 TechCrunch 采访时表示它们很快会推出名为「语音通讯（Voice Communication）」的新功能。Android 和 iOS 将会率先在 2014 年第二季中迎来该更新，而「部分诺基亚和 BlackBerry 设备」则会在之后用上。目前我们还不清楚它到底是怎么个用法，语音频息还是通话，另外，要不要付费呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/24/whatsapp-voice-communication/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2014/02/24/messaging-giant-whatsapp-with-465m-users-will-add-voice-services-in-q2-of-this-year/\" target=\"_blank\">TechCrunch</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/24/whatsapp-voice-communication/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20836613/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/24/whatsapp-voice-communication/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
